The article is a transcript of remarks made by President Donald Trump and Secretary of State Rex Tillerson during a ceremony at the White House. President Trump congratulates Tillerson on his appointment as Secretary of State and highlights the importance of diplomacy and forming alliances to enhance national security. Tillerson expresses gratitude for the opportunity to serve and acknowledges the support he has received. The remarks end with President Trump joking about Tillerson leaving a good job for his new role.